"Death Becomes Her" is one of my absolute favorite movies from the 80's which I've seen hundreds of times thru years, and Sabrina did such an amazing job recreating it here in this masterpiece! The only difference between the two is Goldie and Meryl don't have a kissing scene.  You guys have to now see "Death Becomes Her."
